<topic id="agent_prerequisite" xml:lang="en-us">
  <title>Requirements</title>
  <shortdesc>Prerequisites for agent installation</shortdesc>
  <body>
    <p>The agent can be installed on the following operating systems:
    <ul>
        <li>Windows (from 2000 up to 7 including Server editions), 32 and 64 bits;</li>
        <li>Linux-based systems;</li>
        <li>FreeBSD, OpenBSD, NetBSD, DragonFlyBSD;</li>
        <li>MacOS X (from 10.3.9 PPC to 10.6 Intel)</li>
        <li>Solaris, OpenSolaris, OpenIndiana (SPARC and Intel)</li>
        <li>AIX</li>
        <li>HP-UX (Pa-RISC and IA64)</li>
      </ul>
</p>
    <p>For more informations, please consult: <xref href="http://forge.fusioninventory.org/projects/fusioninventory-agent/wiki/Agent_supportedplateforms" format="html">http://forge.fusioninventory.org/projects/fusioninventory-agent/wiki/Agent_supportedplateforms</xref>
</p>
